'''波尼站'''（{{lang-en|'''Pawnee Station'''}}）為位在[[美國|美國]][[堪薩斯州|堪薩斯州]][[波旁縣_(堪薩斯州)|波旁縣]]的[[非建制地區|非建制地區]]<ref name=gnis/>。

==歷史==
波尼站於1871年設立，當時因鐵路延伸至此站點而設立了此社區。此社區地名取自{{le|波尼溪 (堪薩斯州)|Pawnee Creek (Kansas)|波尼溪}}<ref>{{cite news | url=https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=xdchAAAAIBAJ&sjid=bp8FAAAAIBAJ&pg=2783%2C4254024 | title=Many Towns Have Disappeared (Note: Page loads on 9C due to technical constraints. Scroll to next page) | work=The Fort Scott Tribune | date=July 16, 1976 | accessdate=16 May 2015 | pages=10C | archive-date=2016-05-02 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160502160447/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=xdchAAAAIBAJ&sjid=bp8FAAAAIBAJ&pg=2783,4254024 | dead-url=no }}</ref>。位在波尼站的郵政局於1871年1月31日開業，之後持續營業直到1945年4月30日歇業<ref>{{cite web | url=https://www.kshs.org/geog/geog_postoffices/search/county:BB | title=Kansas Post Offices, 1828-1961 | publisher=Kansas Historical Society | accessdate=4 June 2014 | archive-date=2020-07-20 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200720060408/https://www.kshs.org/geog/geog_postoffices/search/county:BB | dead-url=no }}</ref>。

